---
title: BP Agro — Asignación de Nodo via QR
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor TECH as 🔧 Técnico BP
    participant QRAPP as 📱 App QR
    participant GW as ⚙️ Farm Gateway
    participant DB as 🗄️ SQLite Gateway
    participant API as 🐍 BP Agro API

    TECH->>QRAPP: Escanea QR del sensor Pi 3
    QRAPP->>QRAPP: Extrae machine_id del QR
    QRAPP->>GW: POST /api/nodes/assign\n{machine_id, zone_id}
    GW->>DB: INSERT sensor_node\n(machine_id, zone_id, assigned_at)
    DB-->>GW: OK
    GW-->>QRAPP: Nodo asignado a zona
    QRAPP-->>TECH: ✅ Sensor registrado

    Note over GW: Sensor empieza a enviar\nlecturas cada 15 min
    GW->>API: Notifica nuevo nodo\nen finca (background)
    API->>API: Actualiza inventario\nde dispositivos del cliente
